{"word":"ἀσινής","slug":"ἀσινής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀσινής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σίνομαι'><el>σίνομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>unhurt, unharmed</i>, of persons, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <i>secure, happy</i> of life and fortune, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of things, <i>undamaged</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>not harming</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <i>harmless</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>protecting from harm</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>ἀσινῶς</el>, innocently, <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>-εστατα</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}